---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
const today = new Date().toISOString().slice(0, 10);
---
<Base title="Disclosures" description="Affiliate and editorial disclosures for strmanuals.com. No paid placements. Tax content is education, not advice." path="/disclosures">
  <section class="container-page py-20">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto measure">
      <p class="eyebrow mb-4">Disclosures</p>
      <h1 class="mb-3">Disclosures.</h1>
      <p class="text-sm price-mono mb-10" style="color: var(--color-mute);">Last updated <time datetime={today}>{today}</time></p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Editorial independence</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-6" style="color: var(--color-ink);">
        strmanuals.com is operated by The STR Ledger. No vendor, software,
        lender, accountant, or law firm has paid for placement in any manual.
        Every recommendation is based on first-hand experience or research,
        not on a commercial relationship.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Affiliate relationships</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-6" style="color: var(--color-ink);">
        Manuals may include outbound links — for example, to STR insurance
        carriers, accounting software, or lender resources. Some of those
        links carry a referral or affiliate code. Where they do, the manual
        notes it inline. Affiliate revenue does not influence whether a tool
        is included or how it's ranked.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Tax content is education, not advice</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-6" style="color: var(--color-ink);">
        Manuals categorized as <em>tax</em> are written to explain how the
        rules work, not to replace a CPA. Sample numbers and worked examples
        do not constitute tax advice for any specific situation. Confirm
        every position with a qualified preparer before filing.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Regulatory content</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-6" style="color: var(--color-ink);">
        Permit and zoning material (LGL-01) reflects municipal regulations
        as of each manual's publication date. STR ordinances change often —
        always verify with the current authority before any acquisition or
        operational change.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-3" style="font-size: 1.25rem;">Sister sites</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-6" style="color: var(--color-ink);">
        The STR Ledger operates a cluster of sites:
        <a href="https://thestrledger.com">thestrledger.com</a> (parent brand),
        <a href="https://strhost.tools">strhost.tools</a>,
        <a href="https://strguests.tools">strguests.tools</a>,
        <a href="https://strops.tools">strops.tools</a>,
        <a href="https://strbuyers.tools">strbuyers.tools</a>.
        Cross-links between sites are organizational, not paid placements.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
